headline: AM Best Assigns Issue Credit Rating to Chubb INA Holdings LLC’s Senior Unsecured Notes
summary: OLDWICK, N.J., August 05, 2025--AM Best has assigned a Long-Term Issue Credit Rating of "a+" (Excellent) to Chubb INA Holdings LLC’s (Chubb) (Delaware) recently announced USD 1.25 billion issuance of 4.9% senior unsecured notes due 2035 in the U.S. market, which are guaranteed by Chubb Limited. The outlook assigned to this Credit Rating is stable.
